"use strict";(self.webpackChunkPradocument=self.webpackChunkPradocument||[]).push([[8360],{2999:(n,s,a)=>{a.r(s),a.d(s,{data:()=>e});const e={key:"v-95c9fe96",path:"/knowledge/node/debugger.html",title:"",lang:"en-US",frontmatter:{},excerpt:"",headers:[{level:2,title:"NodeJs之调试",slug:"nodejs之调试",children:[]},{level:2,title:"简介",slug:"简介",children:[]},{level:2,title:"安装node-inspector",slug:"安装node-inspector",children:[]},{level:2,title:"测试代码",slug:"测试代码",children:[]},{level:2,title:"启动node-inspector",slug:"启动node-inspector",children:[]},{level:2,title:"启动nodejs的debug模式",slug:"启动nodejs的debug模式",children:[]},{level:2,title:"添加debugger",slug:"添加debugger",children:[]},{level:2,title:"查看效果",slug:"查看效果",children:[]},{level:2,title:"总结",slug:"总结",children:[]}],filePathRelative:"knowledge/node/debugger.md",git:{updatedTime:1657620056e3,contributors:[{name:"孤城致幻",email:"Xast@123456",commits:1}]}}},3102:(n,s,a)=>{a.r(s),a.d(s,{default:()=>r});var e=a(6252);const t=a.p+"assets/img/debugger.f6dee20b.png",p=(0,e.uE)('<h2 id="nodejs之调试" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#nodejs之调试" aria-hidden="true">#</a> NodeJs之调试</h2><h2 id="简介" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#简介" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 简介</h2><p>当我们只专注于前端的时候，我们习惯性F12，这会给我们带来安全与舒心的感觉。</p><p>但是当我们使用NodeJs来开发后台的时候，我想噩梦来了。</p><p>但是也别泰国担心，NodeJs的调试是很不方便！这是肯定的。</p><p>但是还好，我们有## node-inspector ##来帮助我们解决一部分的调试问题，但是对于异步能力很强的NodeJs它还是有点力不从心。</p><h2 id="安装node-inspector" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#安装node-inspector" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 安装node-inspector</h2><p>依旧是通过npm来全局安装node-inspector</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> -g node-inspector\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><h2 id="测试代码" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#测试代码" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 测试代码</h2><div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token comment">//event.js</span>\n<span class="token keyword">var</span> events <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">require</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;events&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token keyword">var</span> util <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">require</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;util&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">tianxiasan</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">name</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n    <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>name <span class="token operator">=</span> name<span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n    events<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">EventEmitter</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">call</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">}</span>\nutil<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">inherits</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Restaurant<span class="token punctuation">,</span> events<span class="token punctuation">.</span>EventEmitter<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token comment">//定义角色</span>\n<span class="token keyword">var</span> restaurant <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">tianxiasan</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;测试&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br><span class="line-number">7</span><br><span class="line-number">8</span><br><span class="line-number">9</span><br><span class="line-number">10</span><br></div></div><p>这就是我们要调试的代码</p><h2 id="启动node-inspector" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#启动node-inspector" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 启动node-inspector</h2><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>C:<span class="token punctuation">\\</span>Users<span class="token punctuation">\\</span>Administrator<span class="token operator">&gt;</span>node-inspector\nNode Inspector v0.12.8\nVisit http://127.0.0.1:8080/?port<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">5858</span> to start debugging.\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br></div></div><p>好了，启动成功。</p><h2 id="启动nodejs的debug模式" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#启动nodejs的debug模式" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 启动nodejs的debug模式</h2><p>重新开个终端,再来启动nodejs提供的debug调试功能</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>C:<span class="token punctuation">\\</span>Users<span class="token punctuation">\\</span>Administrator<span class="token punctuation">\\</span>Desktop<span class="token operator">&gt;</span>node --debug-brk event.js\nDebugger listening on port <span class="token number">5858</span>\n<span class="token comment"># --debug-brk的意思是使用调试模式启动event.js 并在第一行断点。</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br></div></div><h2 id="添加debugger" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#添加debugger" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 添加debugger</h2><p>在我们需要断点的地方添加debugger即可。会自动断点到debugger的地方。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>server.on<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;listening&#39;</span>, onListening<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\ndebugger\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><h2 id="查看效果" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#查看效果" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 查看效果</h2><p>这样两个程序之间通过socket来通信。我们就可以在我们属性的谷歌开发者中工具中来调试NodeJs了。 <img src="'+t+'" alt="images"> 多么熟悉的界面，下面的调试流程与Js调试差不多。</p><h2 id="总结" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#总结" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 总结</h2><p>第一：使用node-inspector 启动界面调试工具，并在页面打开连接http://127.0.0.1:8080/?port=5858</p><p>第二：使用 node --debug-brk app.js 启动我们的应用,并在第一行断点，方便我们调试</p><p>第三: 如果你想修改代码后，依旧可以热启动，并重新调试的话，那使用supervisor来启动即可，类似这样:supervisor --debug-brk app.js</p>',27),o={},r=(0,a(3744).Z)(o,[["render",function(n,s){return p}]])},3744:(n,s)=>{s.Z=(n,s)=>{const a=n.__vccOpts||n;for(const[n,e]of s)a[n]=e;return a}}}]);